cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image recognition and classification. Additionally, the use of sparsity-based techniques and dictionaries suggests a machine learning (cs.AI) component. The focus on classification and the use of discriminative sparse representations also suggests a connection to machine learning sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the application of the techniques to sonar imaging suggests a connection to robotics (cs.RO) as well.
